original_title: GCW: No Signal In The Hills 2
overview: On July 15th GCW presents No Signal in the Hills 2 live on FITE. The event features the GCW Tag Team Title Match where Team Bussy (Allie Katch & Effy) defend the title against PPRay (Peter Avalon & Ray Rosas).  Also in the lineup:  Joey Janela vs Kevin Blackwood  Tag Team Match  Jordan Oliver & Nick Wayne vs Los Mazisos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)  Johnny Game Changer vs Gringo Loco  Tony Deppen vs Komander  Alex Zayne vs Titus Alexander  Blake Christian vs Starboy Charlie  Dark Sheik vs Cole Radrick
title: GCW: No Signal In The Hills 2
